"function as a service"

no initial investment (free up to 1000 invocations), so it's super great for startups

the IBM serverless solution is open source: https://github.com/apache/incubator-openwhisk

https://medium.com/@amiram_26122/the-hidden-costs-of-serverless-6ced7844780b

the CNCF works on the definition of serverless: https://github.com/cncf/wg-serverless

